name: D22 Navara LED Globe Kit - Interior light, Map lights & Rear number plate lights
description:
For sale we have;
1 x cool white LED festoon for your interior light
2 x cool white large wedge base LEDs for your map lights
2 x cool white stubby bayonet LEDs for your rear number plate lights

Please note - on our test D22 the polarity of the rear number plate sockets was not the same in the left and right side fittings. When testing these globes, if one or both do not light up, the polarity of the lamp holder needs to be reversed. Simply remove your socket, cut both the wires and re-connect them in reverse. There is absolutely no problems associated with doing this, your standard filament globes will still work as they are not polarity sensitive. Just make sure you waterproof your connections with electrical tape or preferably adhesive lined heatshrink.

Thanks!

name: 180SX Type-X LED Dash Cluster & Digital Climate Control Globes
description:
For sale we have a set of LED globes to suit your 180SX Type-X dash cluster & digital climate control!

The Type-X dash cluster has an integral blue tint behind the instruments. The pictured cluster has been fitted with COOL WHITE globes, which still produce a slight blueness through this tint.

Each of these T5 LED globes has 5 x SMD LEDs, which cast light forwards and sideways, making them ideal for the Type-X dash cluster. Each T3 neo-wedge has 1 x SMD LED.

Please note - these globes have a slightly thinner base than standard T5 and will require slight bending of your dash bulb holder pins inward to clasp onto the bulb terminals. This is 100% reversible and does not damage the bulb holders in any way. Replacement bulb holders can also be bought too.

14VDC rated.

name: 180SX Type-X 5xSMD LED Dash Globe Kit
description:
** IN STOCK!! **

Unfortunately for Type-X 180SX owners, Nissan designers chose to use the minature T5 wedge base globes to backlight the dash clusters. Until now this has made using LEDs difficult because they are very directional and subsequently don't spread light well.

We have found a solution!

The new dashled kit for 180SX Type-X features 5 x 5-SMD T5 Globes. That's right - each minature T5 LED globe has 5 SMD LEDs, allowing for better light spread.

Cool white and blue only.

name: S13 180SX LED Dash Globe Kit
description:
Sick of your dull looking dash cluster? Bring it to life with our LED globe kit!

You are looking at a set of 6 LED wedge base globes to replace the incandescent globes in your Nissan S13/180SX/180SX Type-X

Choose your colour from;
Cool White
Blue
Red
Green
Magenta (pink/purple blend)

We supply only super-bright LED products - our wedge globes use 5050 chip LEDs - which have three small LEDs within each yellow dot, making the light output higher than previous generations of LEDs.

Installation is fairly straight forward. Remove dash cluster surrounds to access dash cluster, remove and unplug dash cluster, replace incandescent globes with LEDs and reinstall! 

LEDs are polarity sensitive - meaning that when you first plug the dash back in if bulbs don't light up you will need to remove them from the base, turn 180 degrees and plug back in/re-install the base.
